ut amusing as the security systems go off-line and the dinosaurs escape.","genre_ids":[12,878],"popularity":8.0903,"vote_count":17540,"poster_path":"/maFjKnJ62hDQ9E66dKqDZgbUy0H.jpg","release_date":"1993-06-11","vote_average":7.965,"backdrop_path":"/alqZDg4DXBpNCVTzRPXe5zkkAXX.jpg","original_title":"Jurassic Park","original_language":"en"},{"id":330,"adult":false,"title":"The Lost World: Jurassic Park","video":false,"overview":"Four years after Jurassic Park's genetically bred dinosaurs ran amok, multimillionaire John Hammond shocks chaos theorist Ian Malcolm by revealing that he has been breeding more beasties at a secret location. Malcolm, his paleontologist ladylove and a wildlife videographer join an expedition to document the lethal lizards' natural behavior in this action-packed thriller.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"popularity":0.4862,"vote_count":9061,"poster_path":"/6fSkhv35nPSw9hwPVCMINQFG1WD.jpg","release_date":"1997-05-23","vote_average":6.562,"backdrop_path":"/A4rYaPdzgocCjQ0n9LUSYUxyvpS.jpg","original_title":"The Lost World: Jurassic Park","original_language":"en"},{"id":331,"adult":false,"title":"Jurassic Park III","video":false,"overview":"In need of funds for research, Dr. Alan Grant accepts a large sum of money to accompany Paul and Amanda Kirby on an aerial tour of the infamous Isla Sorna. It isn't long before all hell breaks loose and the stranded wayfarers must fight for survival as a host of new -- and even more deadly -- dinosaurs try to make snacks of them.","genre_ids":[12,28,53,878],"popularity":0.4087,"vote_count":7708,"poster_path":"/oQXj4NUfS3r3gHXtDOzcJgj1lLc.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-18","vote_average":6.172,"backdrop_path":"/8v8x4vVbRgrsdU3M4drnD7HQbfe.jpg","original_title":"Jurassic Park III","original_language":"en"},{"id":15515,"adult":false,"title":"The 7th Voyage of Sinbad","video":false,"overview":"When a princess is shrunken by an evil wizard, Sinbad must undertake a quest to an island of monsters to cure her and prevent a war.